@basePath = /api/v1/exampleSentences

### 1. 分页查询（无条件）
GET {{host}}{{basePath}}?page=1&size=10
Accept: application/json


### 2. 分页查询（按字段过滤 + 排序）
GET {{host}}{{basePath}}?page=1&size=10&queries=sentence:本:7&sorts=weight:ASC
Accept: application/json


### 3. 查询单个例句（将 1 替换成实际存在的 ID）
GET {{host}}{{basePath}}/1
Accept: application/json


### 4. 创建例句（add）
POST {{host}}{{basePath}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "exampleCode": "ex-book-001",
  "sentence": "この本はおもしろいです。",
  "metaInfo": {
    "reading": "このほんはおもしろいです。",
    "romaji": "kono hon wa omoshiroi desu.",
    "meaningZh": "这本书很有趣。",
    "wordGrammarBreakdown": [
      "この：这个",
      "本：书"
    ],
    "fixedPattern": {
      "pattern": "〜は〜です",
      "meaningZh": "A 是 B"
    }
  },
  "weight": 80
}


### 5. 全量更新例句（update）
PUT {{host}}{{basePath}}/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "exampleCode": "ex-book-001",
  "sentence": "この本はとてもおもしろいです。",
  "metaInfo": {
    "reading": "このほんはとてもおもしろいです。",
    "romaji": "kono hon wa totemo omoshiroi desu.",
    "meaningZh": "这本书非常有趣。",
    "wordGrammarBreakdown": [
      "とても：非常"
    ],
    "fixedPattern": {
      "pattern": "〜はとても〜です",
      "meaningZh": "A 非常 B"
    }
  },
  "weight": 70
}


### 6. 局部更新例句（edit）
PATCH {{host}}{{basePath}}/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "weight": 60
}


### 7. 软删除（delete）
DELETE {{host}}{{basePath}}/1
Accept: application/json


### 8. 物理删除（physicalDelete，默认不一定开放）
DELETE {{host}}{{basePath}}/physical/1
Accept: application/json
